import React from 'react'
import './header.css'
import { Header, Segment } from 'semantic-ui-react'
import Search from '../search/search'

function SiteHeader() {
  return (
    <Segment clearing>
    <Header  floated='right'>
      <Search></Search>
    </Header>
    <Header as='h1' floated='left'>
    Book Store
    </Header>
  </Segment>
  )
}

export default SiteHeader
